creator: Randolph-Brooks Federal Credit Union
descriptionHtml:
Your credit union at your convenience!

With the RBFCU Mobile app, your personal finances are easier to access than ever before. Whether you need to check your balance, find an ATM or deposit a check, the RBFCU Mobile app helps you to do it all from wherever you happen to be. Download the app for your device today!

Features:
· Check your account balances
· Make transfers, get cash advances, request money and more using our Move Money feature
· Manage your credit and debit card settings, including freezing your card, reporting it lost or stolen and setting up travel notifications
· Deposit checks anywhere, anytime*
· Stay on track by reviewing your loans and making payments on the go
· Check RBFCU's current share and loan rates
· Pay your bills online
· Conveniently open accounts and apply for loans*
· Monitor your accounts and transactions with customized email and text alerts
· View your current and previous statements
· Find RBFCU branches and surcharge-free ATMs
· Contact RBFCU by phone, email, message, or chat when you need assistance

For Randolph-Brooks Federal Credit Union members. Qualify for membership and join online at rbfcu.org. Federally insured by NCUA.

*Additional qualifications apply to use Mobile Deposit. All deposits, including Mobile Deposits, are subject to the RBFCU Funds Availability Policy. Certain restrictions, including daily and monthly deposit limitations, may apply. RBFCU does not charge a fee for the RBFCU Mobile app, but you may be charged for data by your mobile wireless provider. Loans subject to credit approval and rates subject to change. Some restrictions may apply.

title: RBFCU

creator: Randolph-Brooks Federal Credit Union
descriptionHtml:
Your credit union at your convenience!

With the RBFCU Mobile app, your personal finances are easy to manage. Whether you need to check your balance, make a payment, deposit a check or find an ATM, the RBFCU Mobile app helps you do it all from wherever you are. Download the app today!
Features:
• View your balances, transactions and easily manage your accounts
• Check RBFCU's current rates
• Conveniently open new accounts and apply for loans*
• Send money to — or request money from — other RBFCU members using an account number, phone or email with Move Money
• Deposit checks anytime with your device’s camera with Mobile Deposit**
• Freeze your RBFCU debit or credit card, or report it lost or stolen and more with Manage Cards
• Monitor your accounts and transactions with customized email and text alerts, and set travel notifications
• Access current and previous account statements
• View your loan application status and check for any outstanding items needed to complete your application
• Pay your loans and bills at RBFCU and other financial institutions
• Find the RBFCU routing number and your account numbers
• Request a cash advance from your RBFCU Mastercard(R) or line of credit
• Make domestic and international wire transfers
• Find RBFCU branches and surcharge-free ATMs near you
• Take advantage of your exclusive offers
• Contact RBFCU by chat, secure message, phone or email when you need assistance
If you need help with the RBFCU Mobile app, check rbfcu.org/troubleshootapp for solutions to common issues.
For RBFCU members. Qualify for membership and join online at rbfcu.org. Federally insured by NCUA.

*Loans subject to credit approval and rates subject to change without notice. Some restrictions may apply.

**Additional qualifications apply to use Mobile Deposit. All deposits, including Mobile Deposits, are subject to the RBFCU Funds Availability Policy. Certain restrictions, including daily and monthly deposit limitations, may apply. RBFCU does not charge a fee for the RBFCU Mobile app, but you may be charged for data by your mobile wireless provider.

creator: Randolph-Brooks Federal Credit Union
descriptionHtml:
With the RBFCU Mobile app, your personal finances are easy to manage. Whether you need to check your balance, make a payment, deposit a check or find an ATM, the RBFCU Mobile app helps you do it all from wherever you are. Download the app today!

Features:
• View your balances, transactions and easily manage your accounts
• Check RBFCU's current rates
• Conveniently open new accounts and apply for loans*
• Send money to — or request money from — other RBFCU members using an account number, phone or email with Move Money
• Deposit checks anytime with your device’s camera with Mobile Deposit**
• Freeze your RBFCU debit or credit card, or report it lost or stolen and more with Manage Cards
• Monitor your accounts and transactions with customized email and text alerts, and set travel notifications
• Access current and previous account statements
• View your loan application status and check for any outstanding items needed to complete your application
• Pay your loans and bills at RBFCU and other financial institutions
• Find the RBFCU routing number and your account numbers
• Request a cash advance from your RBFCU Mastercard(R) or line of credit
• Make domestic and international wire transfers
• Find RBFCU branches and surcharge-free ATMs near you
• Take advantage of your exclusive offers
• Contact RBFCU by chat, secure message, phone or email when you need assistance

If you need help with the RBFCU Mobile app, check rbfcu.org/troubleshootapp for solutions to common issues.

For RBFCU members. Qualify for membership and join online at rbfcu.org. Federally insured by NCUA.

*Loans subject to credit approval and rates subject to change without notice. Some restrictions may apply.

**Additional qualifications apply to use Mobile Deposit. All deposits, including Mobile Deposits, are subject to the RBFCU Funds Availability Policy. Certain restrictions, including daily and monthly deposit limitations, may apply. RBFCU does not charge a fee for the RBFCU Mobile app, but you may be charged for data by your mobile wireless provider.
